<item>
 <title>Community Blog Series: Electrolux</title>
 <link>https://identity.allseenalliance.org/news/blogs/2015/08/community-blog-series-electrolux</link>
 <description>
		&lt;span class=&quot;a2a_kit a2a_target addtoany_list&quot; id=&quot;da2a_2&quot;&gt;
			&lt;a class=&quot;a2a_button_facebook&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a class=&quot;a2a_button_twitter&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a class=&quot;a2a_button_google_plus&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;a2a_dd addtoany_share_save&quot; href=&quot;http://www.addtoany.com/share_save#url=https%3A%2F%2Fidentity.allseenalliance.org%2Fnews%2Fblogs%2F2015%2F08%2Fcommunity-blog-series-electrolux&amp;amp;title=Blogs%20-%20AllSeen%20Alliance&quot;&gt; Share&lt;/a&gt;
		&lt;/span&gt;
		
		
  &lt;div class=&quot;field-body view-mode-rss&quot;&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://shop.electrolux.co.uk/file/wCNNQLH/1c726f6d-130b-48e0-bf6a-6010607c06e3.png&quot; style=&quot;float:left; height:58px; margin:5px; width:250px&quot; /&gt;Electrolux, a premium member of the AllSeen Alliance, is a global leader in home appliances, based on deep consumer insight and developed in close collaboration with professional users. Electrolux offers thoughtfully designed, innovative and sustainable solutions for households and businesses, with products such as refrigerators, dishwashers, washing machines, cookers, vacuum cleaners, air conditioners and small domestic appliances.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why did Electrolux join the AllSeen Alliance?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;At Electrolux we develop connected appliances with a consumer-centric approach. This means we want to leverage the technology to address unmet consumer needs.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;We believe the Internet of Things/Internet of Everything has to be seamless and convenient for consumers to use. It has to be built on open, standardized platforms that make it as easy for consumers to add appliances to their network as it will be for new manufacturers to develop connected products. We have therefore decided to join the AllSeen Alliance, to support the development of the Internet of Everything with an open, universal development framework.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What does Electrolux hope to achieve through its participation in the Alliance?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;We expect that integrating the AllJoyn open source software framework will help us to bring more innovations to our appliances, making them more exciting for our consumers. We expect that we’ll be able to work with the various partners in the Alliance to develop new types of services and capabilities.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What contributions is Electrolux making to the project?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;As a &lt;a href=&quot;https://allseenalliance.org/about/members&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Premier Member of the Alliance&lt;/a&gt;, Electrolux will work to develop the uses of the AllJoyn software, integrated in our appliances and together with the services of other partners.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This year, our booth at IFA in Berlin, the world’s largest trade fair for consumer electronics and home appliances, will showcase our vision for what we think the connected home will look like in the future.  We will use the AllJoyn software in our products and show how they can work seamlessly together with other products offered by partners in the Alliance.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;We also support the Alliance through many of the &lt;a href=&quot;https://allseenalliance.org/about/working-groups&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Working Groups&lt;/a&gt; that we participate in, helping to drive the development of the Alliance as well as recruit new members to the Alliance.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Can you describe the Internet of Everything? Can you help us understand how our homes might function 10 years from now because of AllJoyn and the Alliance?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;The Internet of Everything and smart homes will become truly interesting for consumers when we offer products and services that enhance the experience and end result of everyday tasks. For instance, we are working on solutions for assisted cooking which will leverage our expertise gained from working with professional users and world-renowned chefs to help people achieve great tasting food with minimum effort.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Because of AllJoyn and the Alliance, we see even more opportunities for our consumers to achieve great things! The interaction between the consumer and different types of products, in an open community like the Alliance means that not only we as partners can bring new innovation to them, but it also allows anyone with a great idea to develop and implement it.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;How will the work of the AllSeen Alliance impact the industry in the short term? In the long term?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;In the short term the work will allow many partners with complementary offerings to work together. In the long term, the benefit will be for the consumers who will learn to recognize the AllJoyn symbol for the innovation and ease of use that it brings them.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;/div&gt;
</description>
