<item>
 <title>Community Blog Series: Howdens Joinery</title>
 <link>https://identity.allseenalliance.org/news/blogs/2015/07/community-blog-series-howdens-joinery</link>
 <description>
		&lt;span class=&quot;a2a_kit a2a_target addtoany_list&quot; id=&quot;da2a_4&quot;&gt;
			&lt;a class=&quot;a2a_button_facebook&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a class=&quot;a2a_button_twitter&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a class=&quot;a2a_button_google_plus&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;a2a_dd addtoany_share_save&quot; href=&quot;http://www.addtoany.com/share_save#url=https%3A%2F%2Fidentity.allseenalliance.org%2Fnews%2Fblogs%2F2015%2F07%2Fcommunity-blog-series-howdens-joinery&amp;amp;title=Blogs%20-%20AllSeen%20Alliance&quot;&gt; Share&lt;/a&gt;
		&lt;/span&gt;
		
		
  &lt;div class=&quot;field-body view-mode-rss&quot;&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.howdens.com/&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Howdens Joinery&quot; src=&quot;https://www.howdens.com/content/image/1751-4315-3.jpg&quot; style=&quot;float:left; height:166px; width:208px&quot; /&gt;Howdens Joinery&lt;/a&gt; is a leader in the UK market for kitchen and joinery products selling on a B2B basis an inspirational, affordable and available range of kitchens, appliances, and joinery products.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why did Howdens join the AllSeen Alliance?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;As a company we are a leading innovator through service and services for our customers. We must think about the kind of world our customers will be living in in 2020, in 2025 and beyond. How might we anticipate this potential future? How might we play a contributory role in creating it?&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;For some time now Howdens has been alert to developments in the both the idea and practicality of the ‘smart home’. The convergence of interconnectivity and the aspirations that come with the potential for interconnected homes, interconnected communities and cities raise exciting possibilities and opportunities. We are exploring connected appliances and getting these into our marketplace as quickly as possible.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Howdens looked around for who could best help us on our journey and it was very clear that the network being developed by the Allseen Alliance would massively enhance our need for knowledge, understanding, relationships and route maps for creating the ‘smart, interconnected world’.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What does Howdens hope to achieve through its participation in the Alliance?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Some of our hopes have been raised in the previous comments – enhanced knowledge, guidance and connections. Beyond this, we look forward to playing an active and participatory role, where our relationships with our customers alongside the speed at which we can introduce products and services into the market can similarly guide and inform the network.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;We have the ability to bring our experience and relationship with users into the Alliance, adding a breadth of real world scenarios. The future is a more sophisticated proposition, and we want to be part of a community that delivers successful solutions.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Can you describe the Internet of Everything?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;It’s interesting to see how the conceptual language mirrors the exponential growth in thinking about the interconnected world and interconnected living. ‘The Internet of Things’ morphing into the ‘Internet of Everything’!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;There are a couple of things that seem relatively certain to us, if you excuse the oxymoron. Greater interconnectivity in the way we live our lives will fundamentally change how companies and organizations relate to the ‘customer’.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The opportunities that individuals and groups will have to participate actively with our brands will continuously shift; the power and influence that exists in all relationships will continue to favor the customer, to the point where terms such as  ‘customer’ or ‘client’ don’t adequately express the nature of this relationship. It’s started already; just look at the power that a site like ‘Trip Advisor’ yields.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Similarly, as products become smarter and interconnected, they cease to be ‘products’ as we previously knew them. The type and levels of service that are negotiated and offered in the interconnected world become the more salient factor. The paradigm will shift towards how we can fine tune an offer of ‘products + services’ that will enhance what the customer is seeking to achieve with these things. And how effectively we can play a role in ensure their experience of using our “products + services” is a positive and fulfilling one.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Customers have a hard fought budget to spend and we must ensure that what they have bought into isn&#039;t rendered obsolete a little way down the line. We believe that AllJoyn has an important role to play in this regard. Ultimately, we are seeking to participate in the things that empower our customers in leading better lives.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why is open source software and collaborative development important for advancing the Internet of Everything?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;As the world grows ever more complex, no one group or organisation can deliver all the required answers and solutions. We have already alluded to the fact that in an interconnected world, the things (i.e. whatever they might be fridges, phones, lighting consoles) cease to be things in themselves and better defined by their relationship to one another. So, in a way this redefinition demands a new openness and spirit of collaboration. In practical terms, open source is required to ensure that the spirit of development at every level can move forwards unhindered by outdated protocols and requirements.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;How will the work of the AllSeen Alliance impact the industry in the short term? In the long term?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;In the short term, we will look to working with the Alliance to help us move forward in our work on connected appliances and smart living. In the long term, we hope to play a significant role in the Alliance by helping to create a connected world that enhances and empowers each and every one of us.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;  &lt;/div&gt;
</description>
 <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jul 2015 07:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
